And then, Susanna says, a new CEO came into feeding America.

70
00:05:08,294 --> 00:05:11,096
And as usual, what happens when you bring in a pair of fresh eyes?

71
00:05:11,156 --> 00:05:12,537
They look at something and say, hmm.

72
00:05:13,943 --> 00:05:16,664
I can't imagine why you guys are living with that system that sucks.

